Chi is the monk/brawler/martial resource used by several hand-to-hand skills.

Chi cap is class-tiered:
- Base Pugilist (or 20+ Pugilist reincarnations): 15 max chi
- Monk or Brawler remort path (or 20+ combined remort reincarnations): 20 max chi
- Martial adept path (or 20+ adept reincarnations): 25 max chi

Chi is spent by techniques like chiblock, chakra, and spinfist. Some actions
generate chi (for example, many pugilist-style strikes), while others consume
it for defense, healing, burst, or multi-hit pressure.

Flurry converts your current chi into repeated immediate attacks until chi is
exhausted. Some chi skills also become more expensive when used again before
their cooldown fully recovers.

Tip: build chi with your basic chi-generating attacks, then spend it on the
right window (defense, sustain, or finishing pressure).
